  "description": "<i>Hopper</i> is a <i><a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=Frogger\">Frogger</a></i> clone for multiple systems.<br><br>The player controls a young from, who must cross several lanes of busy traffic, and then hop across logs and lilypads in a raging river to to try to get to their home at the top of the screen.  There are a total of 5 homes at the top of the screen, and the player advances to a more difficult level if they manage to get a frog into each of the five spots.  The player has limited time units to get a frog into each spot, or they lose a frog.  The player has a total of 5 lives, and it's game over when all are lost.",
